com.conichi.sdk.dataprovider.rx.impl

Class CNIBaseRxProvider<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.conichi.sdk.dataprovider.rx.impl.CNIBaseRxProvider<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CNIDataProvider<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CNIBaseCloudRxProvider, CNIBeaconRxProviderImpl, CNIRegionRxProviderImpl

    public abstract class CNIBaseRxProvider<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements CNIDataProvider<T>
    CNIDataProvider implementation which provides caching mechanism that saves data in both persistent storage and memory(RAM).
    To cache the data obtained from server call saveEntity(Object)
    If you need to check if an entity is cached use isInLocalCache()
    To obtain the latest saved data use getEntity().
